<i>adverb</i>: 차츰차츰 [차츰차츰], 차츰 [차츰], 차차 [차차], 점차 [점ː차], 점점 [점ː점], 서서히 [서ː서히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>차츰차츰 [차츰차츰]</dt><br>
<dd>gradually</dd><br>
<dd>사물의 상태나 정도가 점점 진행되거나 변화하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of progressing or changing little by little.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>차츰 [차츰]</dt><br>
<dd>gradually</dd><br>
<dd>상태나 정도의 변화가 시간이 지남에 따라 조금씩 계속.</dd><br>
<dd>Little by little as time goes by in the change of the state or level of something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>차차 [차차]</dt><br>
<dd>1. gradually</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 사물의 상태나 정도의 변화가 시간이 지남에 따라 조금씩 계속.</dd><br>
<dd>Little by little as time goes by in the change of the state or level of a matter or object.</dd><br>
<dd>2. gradually</dd><br>
<dd>서두르지 않고 나중에 천천히.</dd><br>
<dd>Little by little later on without rushing.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>점차 [점ː차]</dt><br>
<dd>gradually</dd><br>
<dd>차례를 따라 조금씩.</dd><br>
<dd>Little by little in succession.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>점점 [점ː점]</dt><br>
<dd>gradually</dd><br>
<dd>시간이 지남에 따라 정도가 조금씩 더.</dd><br>
<dd>Little by little as times goes by.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>서서히 [서ː서히]</dt><br>
<dd>gradually; steadily</dd><br>
<dd>조금씩 느리게.</dd><br>
<dd>Slowly and little by little.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>